item.title: CVE-2022-4653|2024-08-03T01:48:38.872Z -- unknown -- greenshift
item.description: The Greenshift WordPress plugin before 4.8.9 does not validate and escape one of its shortcode attributes, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attack.
